cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with human action recognition from skeleton data. The proposed method also involves the use of attention mechanism and graph convolutional LSTM network, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques for video analysis (cs.MM) and the optimization of neural networks (cs.NE).
